J. M. McDONALD COMPANY v. Clive J. LAY. No. 6230. United States Court of Appeals Tenth Circuit. Oct. 19, 1959. Don R. Evans and Wesley H. Doan, Denver, Colo., for appellant. Vincent A. Ross, Cheyenne, Wyo., and Bruce Ownbey, Denver, Colo., for appellee.

Before MURRAH, Chief Judge, and BREITENSTEIN, Circuit Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed on joint motion of the parties., D.C., 24 F.R.D. 36.
